Jika dia tak di sini,
aku tak bisa bayangkan di mana dia.

319
00:25:35,617 --> 00:25:36,447
Gus?

320
00:25:37,577 --> 00:25:39,407
Penyuka Manis, ayolah.

321
00:25:39,496 --> 00:25:43,166
- Berhentilah bermain-main.
- Kau akan terkejut melihat ini.

322
00:25:43,250 --> 00:25:45,040
Gerbong penuh Choc-O-Rockets!

323
00:25:46,211 --> 00:25:48,301
Anakmu pembuat onar.

324
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:49,760
Mirip orang tuanya.

325
00:25:50,465 --> 00:25:52,835
